title: #92Noon! 9am Hour 12/30 - Evason/Larrivee/Vikes
description: Wild coach Dean Evason starts the day with a new contract extension, and then joins our show right out of the gate. Packers vox Wayne Larrivee is next with adversary intel on the Border Battle...the hour ends with "out of body" ideas for Vikes winning Sunday night.
